## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="03e77-104">除非 WMI 类是单一实例，否则它可以有多个相应的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-104">Unless a WMI class is a singleton, it can have multiple corresponding instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="03e77-105">类的客户端必须能够唯一地标识他们感兴趣的特定实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-105">Clients of the class must be able to uniquely identify the specific instance they are interested in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="03e77-106">因此，作为提供程序编写器，你必须选择一个属性或一组属性，这些属性可唯一标识每个 WMI 类的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-106">So, as a provider writer, you must choose a property or set of properties that uniquely identify an instance of each of your WMI classes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="03e77-107">使用 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> 特性来标识这些键属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-107">You use the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> attribute to identify those key properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="03e77-108">标识为键的属性的运行时行为与属性指示的只读属性相同 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementProbeAttribute> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-108">Properties identified as keys have the same runtime behavior as read-only properties indicated by the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementProbeAttribute> attribute.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="03e77-109">下面的示例演示如何使用将 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> 字段标记为 WMI 类的键属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-109">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> to mark a field as a key property of a WMI class.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementKey]  
public int id;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="03e77-110">下一个示例演示如何使用 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> 属性标记 WMI 类的键属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="03e77-110">The next example shows how to use the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> attribute to mark a key property of a WMI class.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementKey attribute to specify that this property   
// is used as the key identifier of this class and for the WMI  
// instances of this class.  This property must be unique for each  
// class instance.  
[ManagementKey]  
public int Id  
{  
    get { return System.Diagnostics.Process.GetCurrentProcess().Id; }  
}  
```
